TITLE: Beautiful Birthday-Borderless
INSIDEVERSE:
Photo Cards are a great way to combine your greeting with a favorite photo.

You'll Need: 4 x 8 1/2 Photo Card Paper.

Directions:

  1. Click Personalize and Print Your Project to open the Creative Workspace.
  2. Make text changes as desired.
  3. Double click on the Add-a-Photo message to add your digital photo.
  4. Click Print to send your finished Photo Card greeting to the printer.
Note: Please follow the print directions on the Photo Card package for exact printing.

Tips:

Print your project on scrap paper first to check the alignment. spelling. and overall look of the project.
